  Purpose:  correct invalid time value
    Notes:  
------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
  IF ipTime EQ ? THEN ipTime = 0.
  RETURN INTEGER(ipTime - TRUNCATE(ipTime / 86400,0) * 86400).

